medqa_ar.doc_to_text:
def doc_to_text(doc) -> str:
    options = doc["options"]
    answers = "\n".join([f"{chr(65+i)}. {option}" for i, option in enumerate(options)])
    return f"السؤال: {doc['question']}\n{answers}\nالإجابة:"
